      "index": "a004o",
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "frameId": null,
      "text": "CartItem.id = cart-local dedup key, NEVER sent: product_<id>_<toppingIds> · combo_<id> · canh_<productId>_rau|plain\ncanh-gate keys off id convention (startsWith 'canh_'), not a type field · CartItem.price incl. toppings = DISPLAY only;\nBE re-snapshots name+unit_price server-side, never trusts client prices.\nREAD: MySQL → Go Details → categoryJSON/productJSON/comboJSON → Category/Product/ComboRaw (TS) → useMemo → Combo/ComboItem\nWRITE: Product/Combo + Topping/Combo modal picks → CartItem (Zustand) → buildOrderItemsPayload → POST /orders",
      "fontSize": 9,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "CartItem.id = cart-local dedup key, NEVER sent: product_<id>_<toppingIds> · combo_<id> · canh_<productId>_rau|plain\ncanh-gate keys off id convention (startsWith 'canh_'), not a type field · CartItem.price incl. toppings = DISPLAY only;\nBE re-snapshots name+unit_price server-side, never trusts client prices.\nREAD: MySQL → Go Details → categoryJSON/productJSON/comboJSON → Category/Product/ComboRaw (TS) → useMemo → Combo/ComboItem\nWRITE: Product/Combo + Topping/Combo modal picks → CartItem (Zustand) → buildOrderItemsPayload → POST /orders",
      "lineHeight": 1.35,
      "autoResize": true
    },
