      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "frameId": null,
      "text": "▓ activeOrderId → null:'Chưa có đơn đang theo dõi'\n  '<id>' → useOrderMonitorSSE(id)\nchannel /sse/order-monitor/:id (DIFFERENT from /order)\nscope: this order + WHOLE floor\nevents: order.status · queue.update(pos=idx+1, ETA=idx*3min)\n  tables.status · items_added/updated/cancelled→refetch\n401/403 = guest JWT(2h) expired → PERMANENT stop\n  → 'quét lại mã QR'",
      "fontSize": 9,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "▓ activeOrderId → null:'Chưa có đơn đang theo dõi'\n  '<id>' → useOrderMonitorSSE(id)\nchannel /sse/order-monitor/:id (DIFFERENT from /order)\nscope: this order + WHOLE floor\nevents: order.status · queue.update(pos=idx+1, ETA=idx*3min)\n  tables.status · items_added/updated/cancelled→refetch\n401/403 = guest JWT(2h) expired → PERMANENT stop\n  → 'quét lại mã QR'",
      "lineHeight": 1.35,
      "autoResize": true
    },
