      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "frameId": null,
      "text": "endpoint: DELETE /orders/:id (item: DELETE /orders/items/:id)\nFE gate: progress<30% AND status∈{confirmed,preparing}\nafter: toast 'Đã huỷ' → router.push('/menu') (guest leaves)\nnever sees the 'đã bị huỷ' modal\nCANCEL_THRESHOLD (≥30% served) → toast\n⚠ DRIFT (owner 2026-06-12): target = cancel ANY time until paid,\n  but code still enforces old <30%+{confirmed,preparing} rule",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "endpoint: DELETE /orders/:id (item: DELETE /orders/items/:id)\nFE gate: progress<30% AND status∈{confirmed,preparing}\nafter: toast 'Đã huỷ' → router.push('/menu') (guest leaves)\nnever sees the 'đã bị huỷ' modal\nCANCEL_THRESHOLD (≥30% served) → toast\n⚠ DRIFT (owner 2026-06-12): target = cancel ANY time until paid,\n  but code still enforces old <30%+{confirmed,preparing} rule",
      "lineHeight": 1.35,
