      "originalText": "FE sends GET /products?category_id&search&is_available (key includes both) but ListProducts has ZERO c.Query calls and ProductList does no client filter → tabs+search re-fetch the same unfiltered list. is_available harmless (service filters anyway).",
      "lineHeight": 1.35,
      "autoResize": true
    },
