      "frameId": null,
      "text": "◀ ComboSection — every ComboCard lists ALL its dishes as ×N lines (always visible);\n   right col = price + [−]qty[＋] + single-select nhân pills. cartId combo_<id>_<nhanId>.\n   'Chi tiết' link → /menu/combo/:id. Shown: 4 combos incl. the Đầy Đủ variants.",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "◀ ComboSection — every ComboCard lists ALL its dishes as ×N lines (always visible);\n   right col = price + [−]qty[＋] + single-select nhân pills. cartId combo_<id>_<nhanId>.\n   'Chi tiết' link → /menu/combo/:id. Shown: 4 combos incl. the Đầy Đủ variants.",
