      "updated": 1746316800000,
      "index": "e0022",
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "frameId": null,
      "text": "Order model  (BE truth -> FE snapshot)\nOrder { id, order_number, table_id, table_name,\n  status: pending->confirmed->preparing->ready->delivered | cancelled | paid,\n  source:'qr'|'pos'|'online', note,\n  total_amount (denormalized · auto-recalc on item mutation),\n  created_by (null = customer self-order), items[] }\nOrderItem { id, product_id | combo_id, combo_ref_id,\n  name(snapshot), unit_price, quantity, qty_served,\n  toppings_snapshot, note }\n★ Combo double-count fix: header row unit_price=0 (combo_id set,\n  combo_ref_id=null); children carry real price (combo_ref_id->header);\n  total = Σ unit_price×qty  EXCLUDING headers",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Order model  (BE truth -> FE snapshot)\nOrder { id, order_number, table_id, table_name,\n  status: pending->confirmed->preparing->ready->delivered | cancelled | paid,\n  source:'qr'|'pos'|'online', note,\n  total_amount (denormalized · auto-recalc on item mutation),\n  created_by (null = customer self-order), items[] }\nOrderItem { id, product_id | combo_id, combo_ref_id,\n  name(snapshot), unit_price, quantity, qty_served,\n  toppings_snapshot, note }\n★ Combo double-count fix: header row unit_price=0 (combo_id set,\n  combo_ref_id=null); children carry real price (combo_ref_id->header);\n  total = Σ unit_price×qty  EXCLUDING headers",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
