      "frameId": null,
      "text": "4 useQuery fire together · all staleTime 5m (no spinner on revisit <5m). Only ['products',cat,q] drives a VISIBLE skeleton; the other three degrade to [] silently.",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
