      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Writes come later: POST /orders → invalidate ['orders'] (catalog GETs untouched).  1-char search disables the products query (no refetch, no skeleton).",
