      "text": "addItem(type:'combo') — dedup by id 'combo_<id>': same id bumps qty, new id appends. ONE combo = ONE line. OPTIMISTIC (the only one in the app — no network wait).",
      "fontSize": 9,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "addItem(type:'combo') — dedup by id 'combo_<id>': same id bumps qty, new id appends. ONE combo = ONE line. OPTIMISTIC (the only one in the app — no network wait).",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
