      "text": "MiniCartStrip → \"1 món · 21.000đ\"\nOrderSummary → preview row appears\nCartBottomBar → total updates\n★ canh gate: items.some(id^='canh_') = FALSE\n  → Bottom DIMMED · OrderSummary will SHAKE 🔴",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "MiniCartStrip → \"1 món · 21.000đ\"\nOrderSummary → preview row appears\nCartBottomBar → total updates\n★ canh gate: items.some(id^='canh_') = FALSE\n  → Bottom DIMMED · OrderSummary will SHAKE 🔴",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
