      "frameId": null,
      "text": "MiniCartStrip → \"2 món · 56.000đ\"\nOrderSummary → adds a 2nd row\nCartBottomBar → total 56.000đ\nAll 3 totals = the SAME derived total() — cannot drift",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "MiniCartStrip → \"2 món · 56.000đ\"\nOrderSummary → adds a 2nd row\nCartBottomBar → total 56.000đ\nAll 3 totals = the SAME derived total() — cannot drift",
