      "text": "items:[ combo…, prod…,\n  { id:\"canh_<Canh>_rau\", type:\"product\", quantity:1,\n    price:0,\n    toppings:[ {Rau mùi tàu, ₫0} ] }   ← stable id drives GATE\n]\ntotal() = 56000      itemCount() = 3",
