      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "frameId": null,
      "text": "★ canh gate: items.some(id^='canh_') = TRUE\n  → CartBottomBar ENABLED ✅  [ Thanh toán ]\n  → OrderSummary stops shaking\nTwo widgets (dim in J, shake in I) read the SAME\nitems[] and reach the SAME verdict — no shared prop.",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "★ canh gate: items.some(id^='canh_') = TRUE\n  → CartBottomBar ENABLED ✅  [ Thanh toán ]\n  → OrderSummary stops shaking\nTwo widgets (dim in J, shake in I) read the SAME\nitems[] and reach the SAME verdict — no shared prop.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "p11-0084",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1676,
      "y": 7940,
