      "frameId": null,
      "text": "Branch reads tableId: ≠null → open TableConfirmModal (popup confirm only). null → router.push('/checkout'). buildOrderItemsPayload(items) — ONE builder, 3 callers.",
      "fontSize": 9,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Branch reads tableId: ≠null → open TableConfirmModal (popup confirm only). null → router.push('/checkout'). buildOrderItemsPayload(items) — ONE builder, 3 callers.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "p11-0094",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 272,
      "y": 8092,
      "width": 840,
      "height": 112,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#E5E7EB",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1746316800000,
      "index": "f0093",
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "frameId": null,
      "text": "POST /api/v1/orders   (NO prices on the wire)\n{ table_id, source:\"qr\", note:\"\", items:[\n  { product_id:null, combo_id:\"<SuấtGiò>\", quantity:1,\n    topping_ids:[],            ← header carries no topping\n    combo_items:[ {Giò×1,[Nhân]}, {BánhCuốn×3,[Nhân]} ] },\n                               ← CANH stripped from combo\n  { product_id:\"<BánhCuốnThịt>\", combo_id:null, qty:1,[Nhân] },\n  { product_id:\"<Canh>\", combo_id:null, qty:1, [Rau] } ] }",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "POST /api/v1/orders   (NO prices on the wire)\n{ table_id, source:\"qr\", note:\"\", items:[\n  { product_id:null, combo_id:\"<SuấtGiò>\", quantity:1,\n    topping_ids:[],            ← header carries no topping\n    combo_items:[ {Giò×1,[Nhân]}, {BánhCuốn×3,[Nhân]} ] },\n                               ← CANH stripped from combo\n  { product_id:\"<BánhCuốnThịt>\", combo_id:null, qty:1,[Nhân] },\n  { product_id:\"<Canh>\", combo_id:null, qty:1, [Rau] } ] }",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "p11-0095",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1124,
      "y": 8092,
      "width": 540,
      "height": 64,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#cbd5e1",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1746316800000,
      "index": "f0094",
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "frameId": null,
      "text": "Store NOT mutated yet — items read-only here.\nTableConfirmModal builds the payload via\nbuildOrderItemsPayload() — never inline (fe/CLAUDE.md).\nSame builder used by checkout + add-to-order → all 3\npayloads byte-identical & match the on-screen preview.",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Store NOT mutated yet — items read-only here.\nTableConfirmModal builds the payload via\nbuildOrderItemsPayload() — never inline (fe/CLAUDE.md).\nSame builder used by checkout + add-to-order → all 3\npayloads byte-identical & match the on-screen preview.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "p11-0096",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1676,
      "y": 8092,
      "width": 840,
      "height": 64,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#bbf7d0",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "roundness": null,
