      "index": "f0121",
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "frameId": null,
      "text": "ShouldBindJSON → 400 INVALID_INPUT on bad body. Per-item XOR guard: each item must have EXACTLY one of product_id / combo_id (neither or both → 400). Maps DTO → service.CreateOrderInput (combo_items → overrides). On service err → handleServiceError; else 201.",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "ShouldBindJSON → 400 INVALID_INPUT on bad body. Per-item XOR guard: each item must have EXACTLY one of product_id / combo_id (neither or both → 400). Maps DTO → service.CreateOrderInput (combo_items → overrides). On service err → handleServiceError; else 201.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
