      "updated": 1746316800000,
      "index": "f0151",
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "frameId": null,
      "text": "GetComboSnapshot(combo_id). Emits a HEADER row: combo_id set, unit_price = formatPrice(0) — MUST be 0 or RecalculateTotalAmount double-counts. Then child rows from the client overrides (each product_id validated ∈ combo, else 400 'không thuộc combo'); child qty = override.qty × header.qty; prices ALWAYS from the server template, never the client.",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "GetComboSnapshot(combo_id). Emits a HEADER row: combo_id set, unit_price = formatPrice(0) — MUST be 0 or RecalculateTotalAmount double-counts. Then child rows from the client overrides (each product_id validated ∈ combo, else 400 'không thuộc combo'); child qty = override.qty × header.qty; prices ALWAYS from the server template, never the client.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
