      "index": "f0171",
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "frameId": null,
      "text": "BeginTx → defer Rollback (any error rolls the whole thing back — no half-orders). qtx.CreateOrder → loop qtx.CreateOrderItem(row) for every header+child → qtx.RecalculateTotalAmount → Commit. All-or-nothing atomicity.",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "BeginTx → defer Rollback (any error rolls the whole thing back — no half-orders). qtx.CreateOrder → loop qtx.CreateOrderItem(row) for every header+child → qtx.RecalculateTotalAmount → Commit. All-or-nothing atomicity.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "p11-0173",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1246,
