      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1746316800000,
      "index": "f0191",
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "frameId": null,
      "text": "After commit (not in the tx): Redis PUBLISH on order:<id> and orders:kds ('new_order') → SSE to the tracking page + KDS. publishAdminOrderEvent (admin board) and a goroutine publishMonitorBroadcast. NO catalog cache touched — products/categories/combos stay warm.",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "After commit (not in the tx): Redis PUBLISH on order:<id> and orders:kds ('new_order') → SSE to the tracking page + KDS. publishAdminOrderEvent (admin board) and a goroutine publishMonitorBroadcast. NO catalog cache touched — products/categories/combos stay warm.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "p11-0193",
