      "index": "f0211",
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "frameId": null,
      "text": "setActiveOrderId(id) → clearCart() → write order_cache_<id> → router.replace('/order/<id>').",
      "fontSize": 9,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "setActiveOrderId(id) → clearCart() → write order_cache_<id> → router.replace('/order/<id>').",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "p11-0213",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 272,
      "y": 9350,
      "width": 840,
      "height": 84,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#E5E7EB",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1746316800000,
      "index": "f0212",
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "frameId": null,
      "text": "STORE AFTER clearCart():\n{ items:[],                    ← wiped\n  tableId:null, tableName:null, ← wiped\n  activeOrderId:null, paymentMethod:null, orderNote:\"\" }\n// persist (partialize) keeps only {orderNote, activeOrderId};\n// items were SESSION-ONLY — F5 mid-order = empty cart by design",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "STORE AFTER clearCart():\n{ items:[],                    ← wiped\n  tableId:null, tableName:null, ← wiped\n  activeOrderId:null, paymentMethod:null, orderNote:\"\" }\n// persist (partialize) keeps only {orderNote, activeOrderId};\n// items were SESSION-ONLY — F5 mid-order = empty cart by design",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "p11-0214",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1124,
      "y": 9350,
      "width": 540,
      "height": 64,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#cbd5e1",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1746316800000,
      "index": "f0213",
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "frameId": null,
      "text": "/menu unmounts — cart now empty.\n/order/<id> paints from order_cache_<id>;\nthe tracking page owns NO cart.\nOnly the ORDER ID (URL) + order_cache_<id>\nsnapshot + activeOrderId crossed the page boundary.",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "/menu unmounts — cart now empty.\n/order/<id> paints from order_cache_<id>;\nthe tracking page owns NO cart.\nOnly the ORDER ID (URL) + order_cache_<id>\nsnapshot + activeOrderId crossed the page boundary.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "p11-0215",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1676,
      "y": 9350,
      "width": 840,
      "height": 64,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#bbf7d0",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1746316800000,
      "index": "f0214",
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "frameId": null,
      "text": "No further BE call on this beat — GET /orders/:id fires\non the tracking page (authMW). The whole order lifecycle:\nQR seeds the store → taps mutate it → selectors keep totals\nin sync → canh gate reads it → one builder drains it into\nthe POST → clearCart() empties it the instant the order is born.",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "No further BE call on this beat — GET /orders/:id fires\non the tracking page (authMW). The whole order lifecycle:\nQR seeds the store → taps mutate it → selectors keep totals\nin sync → canh gate reads it → one builder drains it into\nthe POST → clearCart() empties it the instant the order is born.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
