      "locked": false,
      "frameId": null,
      "text": "• COMBO  → addItem(type:'combo'), one line, price is FE-display, combo_items template inside; on POST it becomes a ₫0 header + priced children server-side.\n• MÓN LẺ → addItem(type:'product'), standalone line carrying its OWN price; dedup by id = qty bump.\n• CANH   → setCanhQty() upsert by STABLE id 'canh_*', price 0 — its id (not a type field) is what opens the Thanh toán gate.\nAll three live in ONE items[] array; total()/itemCount() are derived on read so MiniCart, OrderSummary & CartBottomBar never drift. clearCart() ends it.",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "• COMBO  → addItem(type:'combo'), one line, price is FE-display, combo_items template inside; on POST it becomes a ₫0 header + priced children server-side.\n• MÓN LẺ → addItem(type:'product'), standalone line carrying its OWN price; dedup by id = qty bump.\n• CANH   → setCanhQty() upsert by STABLE id 'canh_*', price 0 — its id (not a type field) is what opens the Thanh toán gate.\nAll three live in ONE items[] array; total()/itemCount() are derived on read so MiniCart, OrderSummary & CartBottomBar never drift. clearCart() ends it.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "p1215-0001",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 9720,
      "width": 1024,
      "height": 22,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#0f172a",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1746316800000,
      "index": "g0000",
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "frameId": null,
      "text": "PANEL 12 · DB row-level view — what the order PHYSICALLY becomes in MySQL  (1 orders row + 5 order_items rows)",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "PANEL 12 · DB row-level view — what the order PHYSICALLY becomes in MySQL  (1 orders row + 5 order_items rows)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "p1215-0002",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 9746,
      "width": 2476,
      "height": 15,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#475569",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1746316800000,
      "index": "g0001",
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "frameId": null,
      "text": "Panel 11 showed the INSERT/UPDATE SQL; this shows the resulting rows. The Suất Giò combo explodes into a ₫0 header + priced children; món lẻ & canh are standalone. total_amount = SUM(unit_price×quantity) — the header's 0 keeps it honest. Source: be/migrations/005_orders.sql.",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Panel 11 showed the INSERT/UPDATE SQL; this shows the resulting rows. The Suất Giò combo explodes into a ₫0 header + priced children; món lẻ & canh are standalone. total_amount = SUM(unit_price×quantity) — the header's 0 keeps it honest. Source: be/migrations/005_orders.sql.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
