      "updated": 1746316800000,
      "index": "g0186",
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "frameId": null,
      "text": "★ Why pub/sub, not direct calls",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "★ Why pub/sub, not direct calls",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "p1215-0188",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 54,
      "y": 10778,
      "width": 2448,
      "height": 14,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1f2937",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1746316800000,
      "index": "g0187",
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "frameId": null,
      "text": "The order service knows NOTHING about KDS, Admin or the tracking page — it just PUBLISHes. Subscribers come and go independently; a screen that's closed simply misses nothing it needs (it refetches on open). If Redis publish fails, it's logged and swallowed (fail-open) — the order is already committed. One write, four eventually-consistent screens, zero coupling.",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "The order service knows NOTHING about KDS, Admin or the tracking page — it just PUBLISHes. Subscribers come and go independently; a screen that's closed simply misses nothing it needs (it refetches on open). If Redis publish fails, it's logged and swallowed (fail-open) — the order is already committed. One write, four eventually-consistent screens, zero coupling.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "p1215-0189",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 10878,
      "width": 681,
      "height": 22,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#0f172a",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1746316800000,
      "index": "g0188",
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "frameId": null,
      "text": "PANEL 14 · Failure & edge map — the unhappy paths Panel 11 only hinted at",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "PANEL 14 · Failure & edge map — the unhappy paths Panel 11 only hinted at",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "p1215-0190",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 10904,
      "width": 2476,
      "height": 15,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#475569",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1746316800000,
      "index": "g0189",
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "frameId": null,
      "text": "Every place POST /orders can deviate from the happy path, where it's caught, and how the system recovers. RED = request rejected · AMBER = silent degrade / retry · GREEN = handled, order still safe. Source: order_handler.go · order_service.go · order_repo.go.",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Every place POST /orders can deviate from the happy path, where it's caught, and how the system recovers. RED = request rejected · AMBER = silent degrade / retry · GREEN = handled, order still safe. Source: order_handler.go · order_service.go · order_repo.go.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
